Work while using my graphics package etc...

- Hmm... this could be a problem, contact @{"me" link ant}.

@endnode

@node bugs "Bugs !"
The only problems I've found myself are.....

- On some modules, particulary ones that have been converted from OctaMED
using AMFC etc... play slower than they should do...

- If a module is corrupt the program doesn't seem to report it, it just
comes up with `File not found'

Anyway, if you do find any bugs, contact @{"me" link ant}.




@endnode

